T*
(- Explain the meaning of Plants in Biology using accurate subject vocabulary.) Tj
T*
(- Describe the key ideas behind roots, stems, leaves, transport, and growth.) Tj
T*
(- Apply Plants to examples such as explaining how water moves through a plant.) Tj
T*
